│ The exit happens from `loop.header`. The value of `%iv` is used in the `return`         │
│ block.\n2.  **Normal Exit:** `%iv.next == 4`. The exit happens from `loop.latch`. A     │
│ constant value is used in the `return` block.\n\n**Symptom Analysis (from               │
